# NUAR Background Palette — DO NOT CHANGE without explicit user request

This palette was explicitly approved by the user. Future agents must not drift toward grey asphalt, near-black, wine/burgundy, or cool blueberry tones.

## Locked hex values

| Token | Hex |
|-------|-----|
| void / cream / mainBg / canvas | `#08060C` |
| surface / graphite / headerBg / secondaryColor | `#0C0A10` |
| card / panel | `#100E14` |
| border | `#1A1520` |
| footer / spa.footer | `#07050A` |
| ivory | `#0A080E` |
| milk / ink | `#E5DFD8` |
| stone / ink-muted | `#9A8880` |
| muted / ink-faint | `#706468` |

## Rejected alternatives (do not use)

- Grey asphalt / neutral grey-brown backgrounds
- Near-black `#040304`
- Cool blueberry / purple-grey tones
- Bright wine / burgundy backgrounds
- Wrong drift values: `#100C0C`, `#161214`, `#201A1C`, `#322A2C`, `#080606`

## Gold accent (separate — can be tuned independently)

- gold / accent: `#B8956B`
- gold-dark: `#967048`

## Gradients & shadows

- Body/surface gradients: warm plum `rgba(8, 6, 12, …)` + faint gold `rgba(154, 132, 88, …)` only — no neutral grey rgba
- Box shadows: warm plum `rgba(6, 5, 8, …)`
- Border translucency: derive from `#1A1520` → `rgb(26 21 32 / …)`

## Source of truth

Keep in sync: `tailwind.config.js`, `src/constants/theme.js`, `src/index.css` (`:root` vars), `index.html` `theme-color`, `public/site.webmanifest` `theme_color` / `background_color`.
